{"tid":2445633,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"龍門幾時肯公布佢啲計劃","createTime":"2021-03-13T18:50:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T10:45:05.000Z","uid":306592,"like":28,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f29f6a0203146b4596ee523333a44e3e1d82e09a","tid":2445633,"uid":306592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T18:50:59.000Z","msg":"邊D租約就完<br />\n仲有幾耐<br />\n打算保留邊間<br />\n放棄邊間<br />\n有咩改善諗法<br />\n大佬買飯卷買得幾多次<br />\n做人要有取捨<br />\n比個知字我地得唔得<br />\n唔係次次都可以俾你告急<br />\n我都唔想你執到一間都冇<br />\n亦唔好諗住我哋會幫你保晒咁多間<br />\n諗唔掂我哋幫手集思廣益<br />\n正視自己問題先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n建議龍門部份分店轉型<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2443499\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2443499</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4898429ff67d2b5db8d714ba9db82ebd79410404","tid":2445633,"uid":306592,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T18:52:46.000Z","msg":"下下淨係識用個撐字<br />\n幫到D咩？<br />\n都解決唔到根本問題"},{"pid":"1ed476c1a30497fc53a2c2c1d18d170e1bd1f570","tid":2445633,"uid":306592,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T18:55:50.000Z","msg":"你咩都唔講<br />\n咩都唔改<br />\n咩都唔提<br />\n我做咩要幫你<br />\n要信你<br />\n下下都shut up and take my money 咩？"},{"pid":"3a92a5f578bbbe4666ad0e2d03ab9c0006b47ea2","tid":2445633,"uid":95499,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T18:58:11.000Z","msg":"佢有plan嘅就唔洗搞到而家咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留返啲錢幫襯其他黃店好過啦"},{"pid":"155ed0bc3a50e8c1f842cb90826ddd4351d7fe61","tid":2445633,"uid":306592,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a92a5f578bbbe4666ad0e2d03ab9c0006b47ea2","tid":2445633,"uid":95499,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T18:58:11.000Z","msg":"佢有plan嘅就唔洗搞到而家咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留返啲錢幫襯其他黃店好過啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T18:58:38.000Z","msg":"將邊幾間分店執咗佢都係計劃"},{"pid":"48d71dc0bb54a20772cab311eb8ce01e73382525","tid":2445633